ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectP.C 1960-1528 and P.C 1963-1803 ** AMENDMENT **
PrecisOrder amending the reserve creation Orders in Council P.C. 1960-1528 dated November 10, 1960 and P.C. 1963-1803 dated December 12, 1963, such that the created reserves are named Kahkewistahaw Indian Reserve No. 72N and Kahkewistahaw Indian Reserve No. 72M, respectively, rather than additions to Kahkewistahaw Indian Reserve No. 72, in Saskatchewan.
